CONTEXT INFORMATION:
"# WayPoint AI Logistics - Website Context Prompt

## **Project Overview**
WayPoint is a modern AI-powered logistics management platform that revolutionizes delivery operations. The website is a professional marketing site built with React, TypeScript, and Tailwind CSS, showcasing intelligent logistics solutions for businesses.

## **Technical Stack & Architecture**

### **Core Technologies**
- **Frontend**: React 18.3.1 with TypeScript
- **Build Tool**: Vite 5.4.19
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS 3.4.17 with custom design system
- **UI Components**: shadcn/ui with Radix UI primitives
- **Routing**: React Router DOM 6.30.1
- **State Management**: TanStack Query 5.83.0
- **Icons**: Lucide React 0.462.0
- **Forms**: React Hook Form 7.61.1 with Zod validation

### **Project Structure**
```
src/
├── components/          # Main page components
│   ├── Header.tsx      # Navigation & branding
│   ├── Hero.tsx        # Hero section with CTA
│   ├── Features.tsx    # Feature showcase
│   ├── Pricing.tsx     # Pricing plans
│   ├── Contact.tsx     # Contact form & info
│   ├── Footer.tsx      # Footer with links
│   └── ui/             # Reusable UI components
├── pages/              # Route components
│   ├── Index.tsx       # Main landing page
│   └── NotFound.tsx    # 404 error page
├── hooks/              # Custom React hooks
├── lib/                # Utility functions
└── assets/             # Images and static files
```

## **Website Sections & Features**

### **1. Header Component** (`src/components/Header.tsx`)
**Location**: Fixed top navigation
**Features**:
- WayPoint logo with truck icon
- Desktop navigation menu (Features, Technology, Pricing, Solutions, About)
- Mobile hamburger menu with responsive design
- "Start Free Demo" CTA button
- Backdrop blur effect with border

### **2. Hero Section** (`src/components/Hero.tsx`)
**Location**: Full-screen landing section
**Features**:
- Background logistics image with gradient overlay
- Animated floating elements
- Main headline: "Save Time, Cut Costs, Deliver Smart"
- Two CTA buttons: "Start Your Free Demo" and "Watch Demo Video"
- Performance stats: 40% faster delivery, 25% cost reduction, 99% success rate
- Scroll indicator animation
- Slide-up animations with delays

### **3. Features Section** (`src/components/Features.tsx`)
**Location**: Main content area after hero
**Features**:
- 6 core feature cards with icons and descriptions:
  1. **Smart Fleet Management** - Truck assignment, capacity monitoring
  2. **Intelligent Package Management** - Digital signatures, notifications
  3. **Advanced Routing & Optimization** - OSRM integration, AI planning
  4. **Real-time Operations** - Live tracking, analytics
  5. **Office & Location Management** - Geolocation, clustering
  6. **Automated Workflows** - Session management, notifications
- Technology showcase: React Native, Django, OSRM, Real-time WebSocket
- Hover animations on feature cards

### **4. Pricing Section** (`src/components/Pricing.tsx`)
**Location**: After features section
**Features**:
- 3 pricing tiers:
  - **Starter**: $99/month (500 packages, basic features)
  - **Professional**: $299/month (2,500 packages, advanced features) - Most Popular
  - **Enterprise**: $699/month (unlimited, custom solutions)
- Feature comparison lists
- Popular plan highlighting with star badge
- CTA buttons for each plan
- Additional info: 14-day free trial, no setup fees

### **5. Contact Section** (`src/components/Contact.tsx`)
**Location**: Before footer
**Features**:
- Contact form with fields: First Name, Last Name, Email, Company, Phone, Message
- Contact information cards: Email, Phone, Office, Hours
- "Schedule a Call" CTA section
- Professional styling with cards and icons

### **6. Footer Component** (`src/components/Footer.tsx`)
**Location**: Bottom of page
**Features**:
- Company branding and description
- 4 link sections: Product, Solutions, Resources, Company
- Contact information
- Legal links: Privacy Policy, Terms of Service, Security
- Dark theme styling

## **Design System & Styling**

### **Color Palette** (`src/index.css`)
- **Primary**: WayPoint Orange (#F39358) - `hsl(22 86% 64%)`
- **Primary Glow**: Lighter orange - `hsl(22 95% 72%)`
- **Foreground**: Rich Dark Blue-Grey - `hsl(215 25% 15%)`
- **Success**: Delivery Green - `hsl(142 76% 36%)`
- **Warning**: Alert Orange - `hsl(38 92% 50%)`

### **Custom Button Variants** (`src/components/ui/button.tsx`)
- `hero`: Primary CTA with glow effect and scale animation
- `cta`: Gradient background with primary colors
- `professional`: Clean border with subtle shadow
- `default`: Standard primary button
- `ghost`: Transparent with hover effects
- `outline`: Bordered variant

### **Animations & Effects** (`src/index.css`)
- **Float Animation**: 6s ease-in-out for floating elements
- **Slide-up Animation**: Staggered entrance animations
- **Feature Card Hover**: TranslateY and shadow effects
- **Button Glow**: Shadow effects on hover
- **Truck Path Animation**: SVG path drawing animation

## **Key Features & Functionality**

### **Responsive Design**
- Mobile-first approach with breakpoints
- Hamburger menu for mobile navigation
- Responsive grid layouts
- Touch-friendly button sizes

### **Performance Optimizations**
- Vite for fast development and building
- Optimized images and assets
- Lazy loading capabilities
- Modern CSS with hardware acceleration

### **Accessibility**
- Semantic HTML structure
- ARIA labels and roles
- Keyboard navigation support
- Focus management
- Color contrast compliance

### **SEO & Marketing**
- Professional copy focused on logistics benefits
- Clear value propositions
- Social proof with statistics
- Multiple conversion points
- Contact information prominently displayed

## **Business Context**

### **Target Audience**
- Logistics companies
- E-commerce businesses
- Fleet management companies
- Delivery service providers
- Enterprise logistics operations

### **Value Propositions**
- 40% faster delivery times
- 25% cost reduction
- 99% delivery success rate
- AI-powered optimization
- Real-time tracking and analytics
- Automated workflow management

### **Technology Stack Highlights**
- React Native for cross-platform mobile apps
- Django for secure backend
- OSRM for route optimization
- Real-time WebSocket connections
- Modern web technologies

## **Development Guidelines**

### **File Locations for Common Tasks**
- **Add new page**: Create in `src/pages/` and add route in `src/App.tsx`
- **Modify navigation**: Update `src/components/Header.tsx`
- **Add new feature**: Extend `src/components/Features.tsx`
- **Update pricing**: Modify `src/components/Pricing.tsx`
- **Change styling**: Update `src/index.css` or `tailwind.config.ts`
- **Add new UI component**: Create in `src/components/ui/`
- **Update contact info**: Modify `src/components/Contact.tsx` and `src/components/Footer.tsx`

### **Component Patterns**
- All components use TypeScript with proper typing
- Consistent use of shadcn/ui components
- Tailwind CSS for styling with custom design tokens
- Responsive design patterns
- Accessibility-first approach

This website represents a professional, modern logistics platform with a focus on AI-powered optimization, real-time operations, and comprehensive fleet management solutions.
"

